snippet: Two suspects have been charged in a shooting at a house party in suburban Houston that left two teenagers dead and injured 19 others, the authorities announced Monday.
abstract: Texas authorities say two suspects have been charged in shooting at house party in Houston suburb that left two teenagers dead and injured 19 others.
lead_paragraph: Two suspects have been charged in a shooting at a house party in suburban Houston that left two teenagers dead and injured 19 others, the authorities announced Monday.

headline.main: Texas: Two Men Charged in Shooting at Party
headline.print_headline: Texas: Two Men Charged In Shooting at Party
